Title: The Lorewalker on the Lake
Description:
Your raft is down in the water below. Take it out to the middle of the lake, where you should find a woman. Her name is Ana  Wu.

Whenever I have a question that I can't figure out on my own, I'll ask her. She should be able to tell us why these crocolisks won't stop attacking.
ObjectivesText: Board your raft, then report to Wise Ana Wu in the middle of Nayeli Lagoon.
RewardText:
You appear troubled, child.

How can this Lorewalker serve you? What is it that you seek?
